1. PROPOSED FEATURES 
<ul>
 <li> Risk Leaderboard: Ranks business units (e.g., "Payments," "Retail") by their security health score to identify the "top offenders."
 <li>  "Production Only" Toggle: A global "safety switch" that hides non-critical environments to reduce alert fatigue instantly.
   <li>Attack Path Preview: A visual node map showing how an attacker could move from a misconfiguration to sensitive data.
   <li>Remediation Effort Tags: Categorizes alerts by "Quick Fix" (Automated) vs. "Architectural Change" (Manual) to help plan the day.
   <li>"Assign to Owner" Button: One-click integration to send alert details directly to the responsible team's Jira or Slack. </ul>
