3. Success Metrics (KPIs)
KPI
Definition
Success Target
Mean Time to Triage (MTTT)
Time elapsed from an alert appearing to it being assigned to an owner.
Reduce by 40% in first 3 months.
Team Remediation Rate
Percentage of "Critical" issues resolved by a team within 48 hours.
> 85% compliance.
Noise Reduction Ratio
Total alerts vs. alerts actually viewed after using "Prod" & "Severity" filters.
70% reduction in "visible" noise for the user.
Feature Adoption
Percentage of users who use the "Assign to Owner" button vs. manual export.
> 60% usage for all critical alerts.


